        <li>Hundreds of molecules produced by the plant that may be biologically active in humans
          <ul>
            <li>Over 100 Cannabinoids other than CBD and THC.  They are all produced as the acid form.  Recent studies have shown both the acid form, and decarboxylated form are biologically active.  Major ones are:
